{"content":"TARGET: InstallationShape (class :Installation), EmissionPointShape (class :EmissionPoint)

IRI PATTERNS:
- Installation: <https://example.org/id/Installation/{uuid}/{issued}/{created}> — substitute {uuid} with localId, {issued} with dc:date, {created} with dc:dateTime
- EmissionPoint: <https://example.org/id/emissiepunt/{uuid}/{issued}/{created}> — same variable substitution

TASK: CREATE 2 instances per class (4 total). Each must be SHACL-conformant per the shape definitions.

SHACL CONSTRAINTS (from shapes):
Installation: rdfs:label (min 1), dc:issued (date, min 1), dc:created (dateTime, min 1), dc:modified (dateTime, min 1), adms:status (adms:Status, min 1), sosa:isHostedBy (:OperationLocation, min 1), ogc:hasGeometry (max 1), dc:type (max 1), adms:identifier (max *), prov:wasRevisionOf (max 1), ssn:hasSubSystem (max *), [inverse ssn:hasSubSystem] (max *), ssn:implements (:Process, max *), :section (:Section, max *), ssn:hasProperty (:InstallationProperty, max *), ssn:hasDeployment (:Operation, max *)

EmissionPoint: rdfs:label (min 1), dc:issued (date, min 1), dc:created (dateTime, min 1), dc:modified (dateTime, min 1), adms:status (adms:Status, min 1), sosa:isHostedBy (:OperationLocation, min 1), ogc:hasGeometry (max 1), dbo:diameter (max 1), dbo:height (max 1), dbo:depth (max 1), dc:type (max 1), adms:identifier (max *), prov:wasRevisionOf (max 1), ssn:hasSubSystem (max *), [inverse ssn:hasSubSystem] (max *), ssn:hasDeployment (:Operation, max *), dc:valid (date, max 1)

EXAMPLE instances:
<https://example.org/id/Installation/INST-001/2024-01-15/2024-01-15T10:00:00> a :Installation ;
  rdfs:label "Cement Production Line A"@en ;
  dc:issued "2024-01-15"^^xsd:date ;
  dc:created "2024-01-15T10:00:00"^^xsd:dateTime ;
  dc:modified "2024-01-15T10:00:00"^^xsd:dateTime ;
  adms:status :actief ;
  sosa:isHostedBy <https://example.org/id/exploitatielocatie/geo-antwerp-001/2024-01-15/2024-01-15T10:00:00> .

<https://example.org/id/emissiepunt/EMP-001/2024-01-15/2024-01-15T10:00:00> a :EmissionPoint ;
  rdfs:label "Stack 1 - Cement Kiln"@en ;
  dc:issued "2024-01-15"^^xsd:date ;
  dc:created "2024-01-15T10:00:00"^^xsd:dateTime ;
  dc:modified "2024-01-15T10:00:00"^^xsd:dateTime ;
  adms:status :actief ;
  sosa:isHostedBy <https://example.org/id/exploitatielocatie/geo-antwerp-001/2024-01-15/2024-01-15T10:00:00> ;
  dbo:height "45"^^xsd:decimal ;
  ogc:hasGeometry [ a ogc:Geometry ; ogc:asWKT "POINT(4.4025 51.2194)"^^ogc:wktLiteral ] .

PREDICATES/CLASSES: Only from ontology/SHACL context. Each triplestore_add is validated as standalone Turtle.
